{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Nu tad / laid ta Kunga\nSpehks pa-augstinahts tohp/ it-\ntin ka tu ruunajis/ un fazzijseffi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS irr pazee-\ntigs/ un no leclas Schehlastibas/\npeedohdams Noseegumu un\nPahrkahpfchanu / kas ne weenu\nnefohditu ne pamett / peemekle-\ndams to Tehwu Noseegumu pee\nteem Behrneem / lihds treschain\nun zettortaim Augnam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Peedohd jelle scho Lau-\nschu Noseegumu/ pehz tawas lee-\nlas Schehlastibas / un ittin ka\ntu scheem Laudim efi peedewis\nno Egiptes.Semmes lihdsfchim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fazzija:\nEs efinu peedewis pehz taiwu\nWahrdu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un nu/ tik teescham ka es\ndsihwoju/ wiʃa Pasaulē taps pil-\nna ar ta KUNGA Gohdibu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo wiʃʃi tee Wihrī / kas\nredsejschi irr mannu Gohdu / un\nmannas Sihmes/ ko es Egiptes-\nSemmē/ un Tukfnesti darrijs ef-\nmu/ un irr mannu kahrdinaj-\nschi definitiskahrt / un mannai\nBalksnet ne irr paklausfiuschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Teem ne buhs redseht to\nSemmi/ ko es winnu Tehweem\nfiveyrejis efmu / ne weenam no\nteem/ kas man irr apkaitinaju-\nschi/ buhs to redseht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet mans Kalps Kah-\nlebs/ tapehz ka zits Gars ar to\nbijts irr/ un irr man pareisi klau-\nfijis/ to gribbu es uhs to Sem-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tohs Amalekitenus/ un\nKamanitens/ kas dsihwo Eeleja-\nBreeseetes Rihta atpakkat/ un\neita us to Tukfnesti pahr tah\nNeedru-Juhras Zeltu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS runna\nja us Mohsu/ un us Aarons/ un\nfazzija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Zikilgi buhschu es peescha-\nniknas Draudses/ kas prett man-\nkurne/ es efinu to Israeta Behr-\nnun Kurnefchanas dsirdejis/ ar k\ntee prett mannu kurne.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Sakki us teem: Tik tee\nscham ka es dsihwoju / fakka ta-\nKUNGS/ ja es jums ta ne dar-\nrischu/ ka juhs eʃʃat ruunajus-\nmannas Ausfs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Schinni Tukfnesti buh-\njuhsahn Meejahm pakrift / u-\nwiʃʃi juhsu skaititi / pehz wiʃʃeen\njuhfo Pulkeein/ kas dtwidesmit-\nGaddus wezzi un pahri irr/ juhs-\nkasjuhs prett man eʃʃat kurne-\njeschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Juws ne buhs us to Sem-\nmi nahkt/ pahr ko es taiwu Roh-\nfu pazehlis efinu/ ka es jums ta-\npar Jhpaʃchunu dohtu / bes ka-\nKahlebam/ Jewuxa Dehlam/ un\nJosuim/ Nunna Dehlam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un juhsus Behrnizus/ n-\nka juhs fazzijat / tee buhs pa-\nLauptjumu/tohs eewaddischu es-\nun tee eepasihz to Semmi/ ko juhs-\npeldami eʃʃat atmettuʃchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet jums / un juhs-\nMe-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
